high_descs: Turn right and cross the room and turn right to face the sink.
Pick up the knife on the right in the sink.
Turn right and cross the room to face the fridge.
Cut the apple in the fridge into three slices.
Turn left and walk over to face the counter to the left of the sink.
Place the knife on the counter.
Turn right and cross the room to face the fridge.
Pick up a piece of apple in the fridge.
Turn left and walk over to face the microwave.
Heat the apple piece in the microwave and remove it.
TUrn right to face the counter.
Place the apple piece on the counter.
anns.task_desc: To heat a piece of apple and place it by the knife to the right of the microwave.

high_descs: Turn right and go as far as the table then turn right and go to the sink
Get the knife that is to the left of the sponge on the right in the sink
Turn around and head to the door then turn left and go to the fridge
Slice the apple that is to the left of the pot in the fridge
Turn left and go to the stove then turn left and go to the table then turn right to face the counter to the left of the sink
Put the knife on the counter to the left of the sink
Turn around and go towards the door then turn left and go to the fridge
Take a piece of apple from the fridge
Turn left and head to the stove then turn right and make your way to just past the sink
Cook the piece of apple in the microwave then take the apple out of the microwave
Turn to the right to face the counter
Put the apple to the left of the knife on the counter
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked piece of apple on the counter to the left of the knife

high_descs: Turn right and head to the sink on the right.
Pick up the knife in the sink.
Turn around and head to the fridge.
Cut the apple in the fridge.
Turn left and go back to the sink.
Put the knife on the counter to the left of the sink.
Turn right and head back to the fridge.
Pick up a slice of apple from the fridge.
Turn left, go across the room, turn left and head to the microwave.
Put the slice of apple in the microwave, cook it and pick it back up.
Turn right towards the sink.
Put the slice of apple on the counter to the left of the sink to the left of the knife.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked slice of apple on the counter.
